 13 |!|
 14 |! PURPOSE:|
 15 |!    TO CONVOLVE THE EQUIVALENT LOAD DURATION CURVE|
 16 |!|
 17 |!  INPUT VARIABLES|
 18 |!    CAPON    THE AMOUNT OF CAPACITY TO BE CONVOLVED|
 19 |!    P        THE AVAILABILITY OF THE UNIT|
 20 |!    CURRENT  THE POINT SHOWING THE POSITION OF THE INCOMING LPROB|
 21 |!    DELTA    THE CALCULATION GRID SPACING|
 22 |!    LPROB    THE LPROBS|
 23 |!|
