 27 |!    ITEMP    TEMPORARY INTEGER STORAGE LOCATION|
 28 |!    SHIFT    THE NUMBER OF INDEX POSITIONS THE LPROB IS SHIFTED|
 29 |!    INDEX    THE LAST GRID POSITION FOR CALCULATION|
 30 |!    Q        THE UNAVAILABILITY OF THE UNIT|
 31 |!  ALGORITHM|
 32 |!    SAME AS PCS MODEL.  BASED ON THE BOOTH - BALERIAUX METHOD|
 33 |!    SPECIALIZED FOR MIDAS|
