1565 |     +                  MAXIMUM_CAPACITY(CONTRACT) .OR.|
1566 |     +                  CONTRACT_ENERGY(CONTRACT)*1.000001 .GE.|
1567 |     +                  MAXIMUM_ENERGY(CONTRACT)/HOURS) THEN|
