1993 |!     LOAD THE LOWEST_COST_CONTRACT INTO THE ELDC FROM B TO|
1994 |!     B PLUS CONTRACT_CAPACITY, OR UNTIL MAXIMUM_CONTRACT_ENERGY|
1995 |!|
