2301 |     +                                 LOWEST_COST_CONTRACT,|
2302 |     +                                 NEXT_LOWEST_TOTAL_COST,|
2303 |     +                                 FIXED_COST_FACTOR)|
2304 |!***********************************************************************|
2305 |         DISPATCHING_CAPACITY = R_DISPATCHING_CAPACITY|
