2335 |     +                     CNTR_CAPACITY_SWITCH(LOWEST_COST_CONTRACT)|
2336 |     +                                                      == 'V' .AND.|
2337 |     +                     CONTRACT_FIXED_COST(LOWEST_COST_CONTRACT) >|
