i:  3039  |     +                            (VARIABLE(82)+VARIABLE(84)) ! TOTAL_CAPITIAL_BAL + STD BALANCE   | 
i:  3040  |         ENDIF| 
i:  3041  |         IF(VARIABLE(82) /= 0.) THEN| 
i:  3042  |            VARIABLE(224) = 100.*(VARIABLE(226) +  ! ANNUALIZED_EQUITY_COST| 
i:  3043  |     +                            VARIABLE(221) +  ! ANNUALIZED_PS_DIVIDENDS| 
i:  3044  |     +                            VARIABLE(222))/  ! ANNUALIZED_LTD_INTEREST| 
i:  3045  |     +                              VARIABLE(82)   ! TOTAL_CAPITIAL_BAL| 
i:  3046  |            VARIABLE(397) = 100.*(VARIABLE(226) +  ! ANNUALIZED_EQUITY_COST| 
i:  3047  |     +                            VARIABLE(221) +  ! ANNUALIZED_PS_DIVIDENDS| 
i:  3048  |     +        (1.-EFFECTIVE_TAX_RATE)*VARIABLE(222))/  ! ANNUALIZED_LTD_INTEREST| 
i:  3049  |     +                              VARIABLE(82)   ! TOTAL_CAPITIAL_BAL| 
i:  3050  |         ENDIF| 
