i: 10025  |                        NEXT_LOWEST_TOTAL_COST =| 
i: 10026  |     +                              10.*CONTRACT_VARIABLE_COST(CONTRACT)| 
i: 10027  |                     ENDIF| 
i: 10028  |                     CROSSOVER_COST = TEMP_CROSSOVER_COST| 
