i: 10033  |!| 
i: 10034  |!           NEXT BEST CL UNIT - CONSTRAINT (4)| 
i: 10035  |!           6/21/93. GAT. TRAPPED FOR 10.*CONTRACT...| 
i: 10036  |!| 
i: 10037  |! MARK QUESTIONS: SHOULD THE ADDER BE IN THIS| 
i: 10038  |!| 
i: 10039  |            LOWEST_VARIABLE_COST =| 
i: 10040  |     +                    CONTRACT_VARIABLE_COST(LOWEST_COST_CONTRACT) +| 
