i: 10067  |     +           INTPL8(LPROB(LD_PTS-1),LODDUR(LD_PTS-1),| 
i: 10068  |     +           CONTRACT_MINIMUM_PROB,LODDUR(LD_PTS),LPROB(LD_PTS))-B| 
