i: 10072  |     +            MAXIMUM_CAPACITY(LOWEST_COST_CONTRACT) -| 
i: 10073  |     +            CONTRACT_CAPACITY(LOWEST_COST_CONTRACT))| 
i: 10074  |            ELSE| 
i: 10075  |               CURRENT_CONTRACT_CAPACITY =| 
i: 10076  |     +            MIN(CURRENT_CONTRACT_CAPACITY,| 
